1
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:12,074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.MY-SUBS.com ]=-

2
00:00:22,303 --> 00:00:23,623
Who is it from?

3
00:00:24,273 --> 00:00:26,063
I cant guess from
the handwriting.

4
00:00:27,212 --> 00:00:28,503
M. Mitra

5
00:00:30,093 --> 00:00:31,903
Must be someone on your
mothers side.

6
00:00:33,374 --> 00:00:34,951
I dont know of any
M. Mitra.

7
00:00:50,709 --> 00:00:52,703
They say, therell be no power
cuts during the holidays.

8
00:00:54,836 --> 00:00:56,783
Well? Whos it from?

9
00:01:10,245 --> 00:01:11,783
Whose letter is it, Mummy?

10
00:01:12,155 --> 00:01:13,503
- Just a moment.

11
00:01:13,943 --> 00:01:17,319
Ok. Like a massive...

12
00:01:20,765 --> 00:01:21,543
Well?

13
00:01:28,046 --> 00:01:30,503
Is it some bad news?

14
00:01:32,303 --> 00:01:33,303
I dont know.

15
00:01:34,472 --> 00:01:35,663
Dont know?

16
00:01:37,702 --> 00:01:39,223
Whos that from, Mummy?

17
00:01:41,303 --> 00:01:42,783
Your great uncle!

18
00:01:44,112 --> 00:01:46,088
The one who ran away from home?

19
00:01:46,165 --> 00:01:47,823
But hes been missing for ages!

20
00:01:49,303 --> 00:01:52,739
35 years! He left in 1955.

21
00:01:53,983 --> 00:01:55,583
I was only two then.

22
00:01:56,259 --> 00:01:57,423
And your uncle?

23
00:01:59,265 --> 00:02:01,263
He left immediately
after graduation.

24
00:02:02,619 --> 00:02:04,263
I dont remember him at all.

25
00:02:06,388 --> 00:02:08,383
Later, my mother told me
everything.

26
00:02:11,072 --> 00:02:13,263
Last time we heard from him
was in 1968.

27
00:02:14,035 --> 00:02:17,263
He never wrote to any of his
relatives.

28
00:02:18,263 --> 00:02:21,824
Only to Mr. Sital. A post
cover every 6 months or so.

29
00:02:22,106 --> 00:02:24,503
From various places in Europe.

30
00:02:25,834 --> 00:02:28,583
It was not possible to reply
because he gave no address.

31
00:02:29,113 --> 00:02:32,503
This Sital was a family friend,
wasnt he?

32
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:35,672
Yes.
He was grandpas neighbour.

33
00:02:35,749 --> 00:02:37,423
He has been to see us also.

34
00:02:38,977 --> 00:02:43,903
Oh yes. He was in the
Governors accounts department.

35
00:02:44,308 --> 00:02:46,223
He has retired and is living in
Shanti Niketan, isnt it?

36
00:02:47,902 --> 00:02:49,903
It was from him that
uncle learnt about us.

37
00:02:50,183 --> 00:02:51,263
Where has he written from?

38
00:02:52,518 --> 00:02:53,423
New Delhi.

39
00:02:55,334 --> 00:02:56,663
Qutub Hotel.

40
00:03:05,571 --> 00:03:08,143
Anyway, just read me
the letter, will you?

41
00:03:10,423 --> 00:03:13,903
I must say his command of
Bengali is admirable.

42
00:03:15,990 --> 00:03:17,642
My dear Baby.

43
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,903
Baby? Who is baby?

44
00:03:20,349 --> 00:03:22,423
Let me read it, will you?

45
00:03:24,559 --> 00:03:26,361
My dear Baby.

46
00:03:26,438 --> 00:03:28,312
I dont know your real name.

47
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:30,743
Oh! Im addressing you
in this fashion.

48
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:32,423
I hope you wont mind.

49
00:03:33,194 --> 00:03:34,823
Thats very florid style.

50
00:03:35,893 --> 00:03:39,903
When I left home, you were
no more than a baby.

51
00:03:39,979 --> 00:03:42,717
I have finished my travels
in the West...

52
00:03:42,794 --> 00:03:44,903
and have only just arrived here.

53
00:03:45,133 --> 00:03:48,803
Learnt from
Mr. Sital that...

54
00:03:48,985 --> 00:03:52,423
youre my only
close relation left...

55
00:03:53,278 --> 00:03:57,423
and are settled happily.
Your husband and son...

56
00:03:57,903 --> 00:04:01,903
I shall soon resume
my wanderings.

57
00:04:02,423 --> 00:04:05,732
In the meantime,
I dearly wish...

58
00:04:05,809 --> 00:04:08,415
to spend a week as the
guest of my niece...

59
00:04:08,563 --> 00:04:11,023
in the city of my birth.

60
00:04:11,802 --> 00:04:14,310
You wont know this uncle
of yours by sight...

61
00:04:14,387 --> 00:04:16,183
as I wont know you.

62
00:04:16,635 --> 00:04:18,863
I realize that in the
instance my request...

63
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:21,423
amounts to an imposition.

64
00:04:21,741 --> 00:04:25,423
In our country,
in the old days,...

65
00:04:25,701 --> 00:04:28,317
hospitality was extended even...

66
00:04:28,583 --> 00:04:31,423
to total strangers.

67
00:04:32,070 --> 00:04:34,329
It is the thought
of this tradition...

68
00:04:34,406 --> 00:04:37,743
that gives me the courage
to make this request.

69
00:04:37,903 --> 00:04:39,418
I have decided.

70
00:04:39,495 --> 00:04:42,903
We leave by the Rajdhani
Express on the 16th...

71
00:04:42,979 --> 00:04:45,903
and arrive in Calcutta
on the 17th morning.

72
00:04:45,979 --> 00:04:49,016
I shall then turn up at
your house in a taxi.

73
00:04:49,598 --> 00:04:52,423
It is certainly up to you
to accept me...

74
00:04:52,628 --> 00:04:55,903
as a guest or not.

75
00:04:56,307 --> 00:04:57,370
Let me assure you.

76
00:04:57,447 --> 00:05:02,903
Im used to experiences
both bitter and sweet.

77
00:05:03,338 --> 00:05:04,841
Yours affectionately,...

78
00:05:04,918 --> 00:05:07,783
Uncle Manmohan Mitra.

79
00:05:08,903 --> 00:05:11,423
You have no memories
of your uncle.

80
00:05:12,223 --> 00:05:15,423
You even recall whether he is
stout or thin or tall or short.

81
00:05:17,223 --> 00:05:17,903
No.

82
00:05:19,287 --> 00:05:23,423
So there is only one thing.
Send an immediate reply...

83
00:05:23,903 --> 00:05:25,983
by telegram, a letter wont do.

84
00:05:39,147 --> 00:05:41,563
Tell him a bare faced lie?

85
00:05:42,278 --> 00:05:43,722
What do you mean a lie?

86
00:05:43,871 --> 00:05:45,743
That people go on holidays...?

87
00:05:45,903 --> 00:05:47,903
Doesnt know Im an executive...

88
00:05:48,479 --> 00:05:49,903
as if I were a professor?

89
00:05:50,223 --> 00:05:52,133
We are enjoying a long holiday
on autumn, wouldnt I?

90
00:05:52,210 --> 00:05:54,092
That youre not professor.

91
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:56,903
How can you be sure that
this man isnt lying?

92
00:05:57,063 --> 00:05:59,183
You know how common fraud
is these days?

93
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:02,823
Theres a priceless art collection...

94
00:06:03,100 --> 00:06:07,326
in that sitting room alone.
Subjects worth a million rupees.

95
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,623
Take just one bronze figurine...

96
00:06:10,183 --> 00:06:12,157
from the top
of the book shelf...

97
00:06:12,233 --> 00:06:13,423
and you can make a fortune...

98
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,823
by selling it to a
foreign tourist.

99
00:06:16,974 --> 00:06:18,903
You mean he is coming
to commit a theft

100
00:06:23,756 --> 00:06:26,143
Uncle was a great
favourite of my mother.

101
00:06:26,637 --> 00:06:28,423
Dad too was very fond of him.

102
00:06:29,493 --> 00:06:30,947
It was not without reason.

103
00:06:31,179 --> 00:06:32,558
Uncle was very gifted.

104
00:06:33,022 --> 00:06:34,903
Never stood second in his life.

105
00:06:39,366 --> 00:06:43,119
Here a person can change
beyond recognition.

106
00:06:43,858 --> 00:06:45,623
It doesnt seem so
from the letter.

107
00:06:48,167 --> 00:06:51,139
Ill assume that he is
indeed your uncle...

108
00:06:51,513 --> 00:06:53,103
and a model of virtue.

109
00:06:53,688 --> 00:06:56,063
Wont you give your husband
a little thought?

110
00:06:57,175 --> 00:06:58,423
What do you mean?

111
00:07:03,593 --> 00:07:06,903
Says hes coming on
the 17th, Friday.

112
00:07:07,578 --> 00:07:09,256
That hell stay for a week.

113
00:07:09,332 --> 00:07:12,183
Means, the whole weekend
would be ruined.

114
00:07:12,703 --> 00:07:14,903
The autumn festival
starts on 21st.

115
00:07:15,903 --> 00:07:17,865
I thought Id relax
during the holidays.

116
00:07:18,131 --> 00:07:19,725
Now comes this old man...

117
00:07:20,049 --> 00:07:21,303
claiming to be your uncle.

118
00:07:28,551 --> 00:07:31,423
Come in dear sir. Sit down.
Have a meal dear, sir.

119
00:07:32,583 --> 00:07:33,764
Dont like it at all.

120
00:07:33,841 --> 00:07:34,983
What?

121
00:07:35,059 --> 00:07:36,743
Your attitude, what else?

122
00:07:36,903 --> 00:07:38,903
You cant send this telegram
in answer to this letter.

123
00:07:39,063 --> 00:07:41,903
As a thoroughly decent letter!
- I dont deny that.

124
00:07:43,047 --> 00:07:47,423
In fact, its a little too
decent. - Thats the trouble.

125
00:07:47,621 --> 00:07:49,365
How can a man whos been
away from home so long...

126
00:07:49,442 --> 00:07:51,423
write such elegant Bengali?

127
00:07:52,903 --> 00:07:56,696
Maybe he got someone else
to write for him.

128
00:07:57,144 --> 00:07:58,423
But the sentiment is
surely his own.

129
00:07:58,500 --> 00:08:01,903
No. Theres a snag in it.

130
00:08:06,004 --> 00:08:07,063
Very well.

131
00:08:12,423 --> 00:08:14,343
Is grand uncle coming, mummy?

132
00:08:16,332 --> 00:08:17,703
Ask Daddy.

133
00:08:22,658 --> 00:08:23,623
What is it now?

134
00:08:27,125 --> 00:08:28,463
Are you cross with me
or something?

135
00:08:43,008 --> 00:08:44,610
A fake uncle is better than
no uncle.

136
00:08:44,687 --> 00:08:48,423
Is that what you wish to say?
- Wish to say only one thing.

137
00:08:49,070 --> 00:08:51,423
Whats the need for a
letter or a telegram?

138
00:08:51,623 --> 00:08:53,743
He says he is coming here
on the 17th.

139
00:08:53,820 --> 00:08:54,640
Let him come.

140
00:08:54,717 --> 00:08:56,077
If I find him a fake...

141
00:08:56,153 --> 00:08:57,854
or he’s real, but has come
with an ulterior motive,...

142
00:08:57,930 --> 00:09:00,183
then you wont have
to do anything.

143
00:09:00,423 --> 00:09:02,423
I myself will whisk him
away with a broom.

144
00:09:06,605 --> 00:09:10,423
Just think - a fake great uncle!

